parameters:
I want to get out of here too, so I guess I have no choice
but to help.

There's a barrier of divine power covering the entire
island, making it undetectable from afar.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]Oh my. But the Seraphic Bless communications do get through.

That's probably because... that device is accessing the
divine power communication channels used by this lab without
permission. Such incredible technology...

I see, I was wondering why GPS communications didn't work
but divine power communications did... So it's using the
lab's channel to communicate with the outside...

...It means that Yuri-san's company has amazing
technological capabilities.

Anyway!! If we don't stop that barrier, it will be difficult
to pinpoint that location!
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]So we just need to break the barrier, right?!

If you want to stop the barrier, you should probably check
the director's office. The director of this lab should be
managing it.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Alright, the director's office it is! Let's go!!

The director's office is on the 30th floor of this building.
You should use the elevator for the upper floors next to the
one that goes to the basement floors.\C[0]
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Got it! The elevator for the upper floors!\C[0]
'30Fの所長室でバリアを解除する'

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Right! Do you know where this laboratory is located, big
brother?

Unfortunately, even we researchers are not informed of where
this place is.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]I remember reading in a book that you can calculate your
current location based on the position of the sun and stars
and stuff...

Unfortunately... there seems to be a function in the barrier
surrounding the island that refracts the scenery... It's
been made so that we can't measure our location.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]So they've got it all covered, huh...

The director's office is on the 30th floor of this building.
You should use the elevator for the upper floors \C[2]next
to the one that goes to the basement floors\C[0].
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Got it! The elevator for the upper floors \C[2]it is\C[0]!
I can't see in front of me... Whoa!
Phew... That was a terrible experience...

An island... So we were taken all the way to a place like
this... Could it have been by boat or airplane, I wonder...

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Anyway, if I release my divine power here, do you think we
can pinpoint our location?
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A
It seems there are no traps in this area.

If you're going to interfere with the garbage collection,
then you are garbage too. Garbage will be collected.
